extends base

block content
  main.main
    section.hero.hero--about
      .container
        .hero__content
          h1.hero__title About Bedvan Tours
          p.hero__subtitle Discover the story behind our adventure company
          a.btn.btn--primary(href='/') Back to Home
    
    .container
      section.about-section
        .about-content
          h2.about-section__title Our Story
          p.about-section__text.
            Bedvan Tours was founded with a passion for adventure and a commitment to providing 
            unforgettable experiences for travelers around the world. Our team of local experts 
            knows the hidden gems and secret spots that make each destination truly special.
          
          p.about-section__text.
            Since our inception, we've been dedicated to sustainable tourism, supporting local 
            communities, and preserving the natural beauty of the places we visit. Every tour 
            we offer is carefully crafted to provide an authentic experience while minimizing 
            environmental impact.
          
          h2.about-section__title Our Mission
          p.about-section__text.
            Our mission is to connect travelers with the world's most breathtaking destinations 
            through expertly guided tours that are both educational and exhilarating. We believe 
            in creating memories that last a lifetime while fostering a deep appreciation for 
            different cultures and environments.
          
          h2.about-section__title Why Choose Us
          .features
            .feature-card
              i.fas.fa-map-marked-alt.feature-card__icon
              h3.feature-card__title Expert Guides
              p.feature-card__text.
                Our local guides are passionate experts who bring destinations to life with their 
                knowledge and storytelling.
            
            .feature-card
              i.fas.fa-heart.feature-card__icon
              h3.feature-card__title Small Groups
              p.feature-card__text.
                We keep our groups small to ensure personalized attention and a more intimate 
                travel experience.
            
            .feature-card
              i.fas.fa-leaf.feature-card__icon
              h3.feature-card__title Sustainable Travel
              p.feature-card__text.
                We're committed to responsible tourism that benefits local communities and 
                preserves natural environments.